Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 阿土就一直看着杏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人一直在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样子好奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土救我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏被人盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:01:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有个很可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没关系的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是小梅的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸应援团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不去学校吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大学放假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}妹控…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以过来看看小梅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅在这里过得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父 不愧是您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在幼稚园内拍照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只拍你妹妹的话是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅的小裤裤是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友之间这样是家常便饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道我太过于操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那孩子太过老实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实昨天也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第10届 花丸幼稚园 运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 幼稚园的运动会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好那天我也能去加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥要来运动会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是准备去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你不开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅肯定会跑倒数的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就一直很消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小梅确实跑得有点慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的跑了倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅肯定会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 练习跑步不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在讨论很严重的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅想要练习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们需要一个教练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我跑得也不快 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 由草野老师来指导的话 会进步得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说小梅是因为不想让哥哥担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才决定要加油练习跑步的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场景太燃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让小梅取得第一名的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们志在全国高中运动会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要记住正确的跑步方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会快起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们立刻开始特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是一边摆动手臂一边跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记摆臂慢慢跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体稍稍前倾 下巴向前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 跑得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明天吧 运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1到3名都可以得到奖牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅也能得到奖牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天就请大家尽情地跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要注意不要受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是佑君和贤治君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 不给贤治君加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤治君 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父 我听到您为我加油的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了回报您 我会跑第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是轻而易举 这种程度的障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 雏菊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 嘿 雏菊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 嘿 雏 菊 嘿 嘿 雏 菊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 您光是站着就很醒目了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以应援请您低调点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 赛跑差不多快开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去起跑线集合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 一直在进行跑步的练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定真的能跑第一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我跑的速度也跟小梅差不多慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 却没人为我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没留意到你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不会引人注意的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的英雄就是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭 你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年再加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅在第一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定真的能拿到奖牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大概是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能拍手！不能拍手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持到最后了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是家人最好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然哥哥做得不怎么好看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 小梅是最后一名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持到最后的小梅和跑第一名一样厉害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 小梅周围的人都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次运动会一定要好好表现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很久没举行联欢会了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么而干杯好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周是西风老师的生日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就来庆祝西风老师的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}花丸告白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 山本老师也看漫画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 前几天从妹妹那借的漫画也非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「恋爱 Step」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是「恋爱 Step」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 嗯 看了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能搭话 回去补补吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你是说全都是我们不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是老师也有做不成的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水主川老师居然醉成这样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 只要工作就会有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了解除压力才开联欢会的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师 你也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚来幼稚园的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你肯定很没用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:13:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最近变得有那么一点点可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们大家去下一家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 土田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被三个美女包围着真是幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏和雏菊又那么喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是超受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还缺少点肌肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个肌肉控
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 巨乳控
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然喜欢大胸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们在山本老师面前不要说这种话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土 撒身上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土？山本老师喝醉了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师给你擦一擦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个莫非就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师 告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狭窄的房间里 年轻的男女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且菜菜还是那个状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你能行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师也有很多优点的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是陪我一块看录影带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也叫优点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行能行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 说出一直藏在心里的那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是最痛苦还是最快乐的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意让我陪你一起度过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田 说得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了 说了 告白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了 说了 告白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了 说了 告白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上又迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又熬夜玩游戏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要只是那样的话该多好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 要是可以的话能跟我说说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 心意我领了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然昨天借着酒劲告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在听到山本老师回答之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就醉得神志不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后今天早上因为没脸见人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就迟到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然很糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事还是不要告诉小杏比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏菊也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起来玩过家家游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土扮演杏的老公哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏菊也想扮演新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 土田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为昨天的「那个」…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 昨天玩得真开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草野老师 关于昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师说什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也不是很想听…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上根本没提那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要自己去问的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天喝完酒还没缓过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你拿点药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师 老实问就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说昨天土田大人和山本老师之间发生了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草野老师您清楚的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦 也不是什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不算什么大事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也请告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们已经有觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草野老师千万不要说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}所以请告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然解释起来就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天土田老师向山本老师告白了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土向…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师 告白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过虽说是告白了 也不一定就要交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师还没回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没回答…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才那个态度来看…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 居然甩掉了像土田大人这样优秀的男士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师真是没有眼光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说阿土很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是追山本老师还是很勉强的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了？勉强？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏会一直陪在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田大人 请打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有雏菊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是Happy End？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这还没完…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是怎么了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 山本老师好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很在意 但是又不能进去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师也要结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要结婚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是拍了一下照片而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天陪朋友去试婚纱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很适合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来有一天 我也能穿上婚纱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不想把她让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我昨天说的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句台词
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「恋爱 Step」里的经典台词呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜欢那句台词了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以看到土田老师能像电视剧一样 将它帅气地演绎出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要被人那样告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看那部漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 下次借给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}谢谢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 她忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拓海 一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这个人是相当地迟钝啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错啦 至少没被甩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟被甩差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 这一辈子都察觉不到我的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起呢 早上就让你吃便利店的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏最喜欢三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等手头的工作告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好好做饭给你吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身酒臭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝得不省人事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 樱前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你遇到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要活着总有不顺心的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想去幼稚园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是辞掉工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的人辞掉也没人在乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是土田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 樱前辈还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天是我不对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 明天要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 最后就拜托杏了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周讲的是送上门的老婆和花丸故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}花丸送上门的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}花丸故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:19.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さわったらね　だめだっていうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:23.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かたまらなくて、いたい　雨あがりのハート
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:28.16,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみが揺らした恋の　真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:31.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水の　冠って、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:36.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すてきなもの　おとしてくから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:41.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面張力　あふれだすんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:48.55,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,オモチャ箱の夢たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:52.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:58.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追いかけて　転んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:02.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひっしだった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:06.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの日も今も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:14.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わらって　つかめるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:19.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来は　その手に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:25.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽根のように　舞い降りる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:19.14,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不能碰这碰那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:23.71,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么死板 放晴的心情 有点失落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:28.16,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在因你摇晃的恋爱的正中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:31.10,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溅起了如皇冠般的水花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:36.29,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的东西 总是会逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:41.09,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面张力 洋溢出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:48.55,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具箱的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:52.89,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:58.11,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力追赶 即使摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:02.32,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论哪一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:06.59,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:14.95,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑吧 我们能把握
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:19.36,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那宛如羽毛般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:25.84,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘落的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【STAFF】
